data.description: Discover your dream home! This 3BR, 2BA gem offers a 2-car garage, new A/C, and 2-year-old roof. Inside, enjoy modern appliances, a security system, and 3 included TVs. The open floor plan is perfect for hosting, and a serene lake view awaits in the backyard. Low HOA fees sweeten the deal. Don't forget the generator hookup for added convenience. This property blends updates, space, and charm, making it a comfortable and luxurious haven. Make it yours today!''
